Task 4: Predicting Insurance Claim Amounts

Estimating medical insurance claim amounts using Machine Learning.

Objective
● Cleaned the Medical Cost Personal dataset.
● Encoded categorical features like Sex, Smoker, and Region.
● Trained a Linear Regression model.
● Visualized and analyzed how BMI, Age, and Smoking status impact insurance charges.

Model Performance
● Accuracy: 78% (R² Score)
● Error Metrics: MAE ($4,181) and RMSE ($5,796)
● Top Influencers: Smoking Status, Age, and BMI.
